flowchart TD
    Start([New engine: SQL Server / MySQL / SQLite]) --> Caps{Declare capabilities}

    Caps --> WriteCaps[Implement IWorkCoordinatorCapabilities<br/>EngineName / SupportsServerSideNotifications /<br/>SupportsBulkCopy / SupportsAdvisoryLocks /<br/>SupportsNativeArrayParameters / SupportsListenOverPooler /<br/>SupportsSavepoints]

    WriteCaps --> Coord[Implement IWorkCoordinator]
    Coord --> CoordMethods[10 methods<br/>Default-throws on interface — implement what you need:<br/>RecordHeartbeatAsync / ClaimWorkAsync /<br/>CommitHandlerResultAsync / CommitHandlerBatchAsync /<br/>CompleteOutboxPublishedAsync / CompletePerspectiveAsync /<br/>RenewLeasesAsync / ReportFailuresAsync /<br/>FlushCompletionsAsync / ResolveSyncInquiriesAsync]

    CoordMethods --> SQLContracts[Map to engine SQL functions per sql-function-contracts]

    SQLContracts --> Notif{SupportsServerSideNotifications?}
    Notif -->|yes| WriteListener[Implement IWorkNotificationListener<br/>OnSignal + OnHealthChanged + IsHealthy<br/>Reconnect + keepalive contract]
    Notif -->|no| NoOpListener[Bind NoOpWorkNotificationListener<br/>System runs polling-only]

    WriteListener --> AppSignals{App-level pub/sub wanted?}
    NoOpListener --> Register
    AppSignals -->|yes| WriteAppSig[Implement IAppSignalChannel]
    AppSignals -->|no| NoOpApp[Bind NoOpAppSignalChannel]

    WriteAppSig --> Register
    NoOpApp --> Register

    Register[Register via DI extension<br/>AddWhizbang...EngineName]
    Register --> Tests[Run conformance test suite]
    Tests --> Pass{All pass?}
    Pass -->|yes| Done([Engine ready])
    Pass -->|no| Debug[Iterate]
    Debug --> Coord

    classDef required fill:#efe,stroke:#3c3,stroke-width:2px
    classDef optional fill:#eef,stroke:#33c,stroke-width:1px,stroke-dasharray:4
    classDef terminal fill:#fff,stroke:#000,stroke-width:2px
    class WriteCaps,Coord,CoordMethods,SQLContracts,Register,Tests required
    class WriteListener,NoOpListener,WriteAppSig,NoOpApp optional
    class Start,Done terminal
